graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager<br/>Operator]
        ControllerMetrics["metrics endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP"]
        ControllerHealth["healthz, readyz<br/>8081/TCP HTTP"]
        Controller -->|exposes| ControllerMetrics
        Controller -->|exposes| ControllerHealth
    end

    subgraph "DSPA Instance Components (per namespace)"
        APIServer[DS Pipelines API Server<br/>Deployment]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Deployment]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Deployment]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Deployment - Argo]

        subgraph "Optional Components"
            MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>StatefulSet]
            Minio[Minio<br/>Deployment - S3]
            MLMDGRPC[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>Deployment]
            MLMDEnvoy[ML Metadata Envoy<br/>Deployment - Proxy]
            PipelinesUI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>Deployment]
        end
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates & manages| APIServer
    Controller -->|creates & manages| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|creates & manages| ScheduledWF
    Controller -->|creates & manages| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|creates & manages| MariaDB
    Controller -->|creates & manages| Minio
    Controller -->|creates & manages| MLMDGRPC
    Controller -->|creates & manages| MLMDEnvoy
    Controller -->|creates & manages| PipelinesUI

    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|creates| WorkflowCR[Workflow CR<br/>Argo]
    WorkflowController -->|watches| WorkflowCR
    WorkflowController -->|creates| PipelinePods[Pipeline Execution Pods]

    PipelinePods -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    PipelinePods -->|tracks lineage| MLMDGRPC

    PersistenceAgent -->|syncs workflow state| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|queries| APIServer

    ScheduledWF -->|creates| ScheduledWorkflowCR[ScheduledWorkflow CR]
    ScheduledWorkflowCR -->|triggers| WorkflowCR

    MLMDGRPC -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies to| MLMDGRPC

    %% External Dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows 3.x<br/>embedded]
    APIServer -->|OAuth via| OAuthProxy[OpenShift OAuth]
    PipelinesUI -->|OAuth via| OAuthProxy
    Controller -->|integrates| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Services
    PipelinePods -->|can use| ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    APIServer -->|can use| ExternalDB[External MySQL DB<br/>3306/TCP TLS]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WorkflowController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MariaDB fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Minio fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ArgoWorkflows fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ODHDashboard fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
